    <hr />
    <p>This is QUT Surfers first learn to surf weekend for the semester. We have got you covered for everything you need. QUT Surfers and Soul Surf School will be taking a lucky 60 people down to Byron Bay over the weekend for an awesome full weekend of surfing, exploring and partying. The package includes:</p>
