    <hr />
    <p class="w3-justify">
        <strong>Friday DAY 1:</strong><br />
        Arrive 2:30 pm at bus stop 69A Alice street QUT Gardens point. Do not be late as the bus could depart without you. Departure is 3 pm sharp.<br />
        Arrive in Byron Bay that afternoon.<br />
        BBQ and vibes on at the accommodation before we head out for a Paint Party, (pack clothes you can get paint on).<br /> <br />

        <strong>Saturday DAY 2:</strong><br />
        Breakfast included<br /> Split into groups - one group will surf, while the other groups explores Byron bay.<br />
        While exploring Byron, grab some lunch at a local cafe or the shops.<br />
        Rotate groups - Next group Surfs, first group explores.<br />
        Pizza Dinner included with a pub crawl organised and run by the QUT Surfers Team.<br /> <br />

        <strong>Sunday DAY 3:</strong><br />
        Rinse and Repeat of Saturday but depart Byron at around 6pm.<br />
        Find your own dinner.<br /> Return to QUT around 7-8pm.<br /> <br />
    <hr />
    <h4 class="w3-justify"><strong>WHAT TO BRING</strong></h4>
    <hr />
        Appropriate clothing for a full weekend, Including:<br />
        Going out party (dress codes not super strict)<br />
        Clothes you can get paint on at the Paint Party for friday night!<br />
        Casual Day clothes<br /> Towel, Sunscreen and Water bottle<br />
        Don't forget extra spending money for around Byron and drinks!<br />
    <span style="color: #ff0000;"><u>Bring ID!!!</u></span><br /> 
